// Template for Config.local.xcconfig.
// Copy this file to Config.local.xcconfig and fill in your backend base URL:
//
//   cp Config.example.xcconfig Config.local.xcconfig
//
// Config.xcconfig includes Config.local.xcconfig when present, so its
// BASE_URL overrides the committed empty default. The value feeds
// INFOPLIST_KEY -> Info.plist, which AppConfiguration reads at launch.
//
// Note: xcconfig treats "//" as a comment, so the $() empty-expansion
// splits the URL's slashes to keep "https://" intact.
BASE_URL = https:/$()/your-backend-host.example.com/
